rows.label: tlk70000046_04_msg0001
rows.name:
Hey there. A lot of people round these
parts have a lot of nice things to say
about you.

rows.label: tlk70000046_04_msg0002
rows.name:
Sounds like you've been solving
problems and taking on requests
from folks?

rows.label: tlk70000046_04_msg0003
rows.name:
Darn, used to be, I was the go-to
dogsbody around here. I must've
let myself get complacent!

rows.label: tlk70000046_04_msg0004
rows.name: Oh, uh, but don't get me wrong, OK?

rows.label: tlk70000046_04_msg0005
rows.name:
It's not like I'm gonna enter into some
kind of helping-out competition with
all of you, all right? I'm not an idiot.

rows.label: tlk70000046_04_msg0006
rows.name:
I'm plenty glad that my neighbors
are living healthier and happier lives
thanks to you, that's really enough.
